{// Simple track to suppress outputs.
    val numericalColumns = spark.table("survey").dtypes.filter(_._2 != "StringType").map(_._1)
    val categoricalColumns = spark.table("survey").dtypes.filter(_._2 == "StringType").map(_._1)
    
    val numBins = z.textbox("막대 개수", "10").toString
    val selectedColumn = z.select("컬럼", numericalColumns(0), numericalColumns.map(x => (x, x))).toString
    val selectedGroup = z.select("그룹", categoricalColumns(0), categoricalColumns.map(x => (x, x))).toString
    
    z.angularBind("numBins", numBins) // Override the dynamic form "numBins".
    z.angularBind("column", selectedColumn)   // Override the dynamic form "column".
    z.angularBind("group", selectedGroup)
    
    z.run("20180519-003745_400359499")  // !!! Copy and paste your paragraph ID!
    
    val numRows = spark.table("survey").count()
    val values = spark.table("survey").select(selectedColumn)
    
    val avg = values.selectExpr(s"AVG(${selectedColumn})").first.getDouble(0)
    val numMissingValues = values.where(s"${selectedColumn} IS NULL").count()
    val missingRate = 1.0 * numMissingValues / numRows
    val fontSize = (missingRate * 100).toInt
    
    z.angularBind("average", avg.toString)
    z.angularBind("fontSize", fontSize)
    z.angularBind("missingRate", missingRate)

    z.run("20180519-012245_1766247646")
}

%sql
WITH
target (
SELECT
    ${column} AS x,
    ${group} AS grp
FROM survey
WHERE ${column} IS NOT NULL  -- NULL 제거
),
stats (
SELECT
    MIN(x) AS x_min,
    ${numBins} AS num_bins,
    (MAX(x) - MIN(x)) / ${numBins} AS bin_width  -- bin 너비 계산
FROM target
),
bin_tmp (
SELECT
    x, grp,
    FLOOR((x - x_min) / bin_width) AS bin  -- 각 값이 어느 bin에 속하는지 계산
FROM
    target
    CROSS JOIN stats
),
bin (
SELECT
    x, grp, 
    CASE WHEN bin = num_bins THEN num_bins - 1 ELSE bin END AS bin  -- 마지막 bin의 범위를 90 ~ 99이 아닌 90 ~ 100이 되도록
FROM
    bin_tmp
    CROSS JOIN stats
),
bin_stats (  -- 각 bin의 여러 통계량 계산 (x축에 나타낼 값들)
SELECT
    bin,
    AVG(x) AS bin_avg,
    MIN(x) AS bin_min,
    MAX(x) AS bin_max,
    MIN(bin_width) * bin AS bin_start,
    MIN(bin_width) * (bin + 1) AS bin_end
FROM
    bin
    CROSS JOIN stats
GROUP BY bin
),
bin_grp (
SELECT
    bin, grp, COUNT(*) AS bin_grp_cnt
FROM bin
GROUP BY bin, grp
)
SELECT bin, grp, bin_grp_cnt, bin_avg, bin_min, bin_max, bin_start, bin_end
FROM
    bin_grp
    JOIN bin_stats USING (bin)
ORDER BY bin, grp

{// Simple track to suppress outputs.
    val categoricalColumns = spark.table("survey").dtypes.filter(_._2 == "StringType").map(_._1)
    
    val limit = z.textbox("Category 개수", "10").toString
    val selectedColumn = z.select("컬럼", categoricalColumns(0), categoricalColumns.map(x => (x, x)))
    val selectedGroup = z.select("그룹", categoricalColumns(0), categoricalColumns.map(x => (x, x)))
    
    z.angularBind("limit", limit) // Override the dynamic form "numBins".
    z.angularBind("column", selectedColumn)   // Override the dynamic form "column".
    z.angularBind("group", selectedGroup)
    
    z.run("20180519-011149_794588296")  // !!! Copy and paste your paragraph ID!
}

%sql
WITH
target (
SELECT
    ${column} AS x,
    ${group} AS grp
FROM survey
),
grp_cnt (
SELECT x, grp, COUNT(*) AS grp_cnt
FROM target
GROUP BY x, grp
),
x_cnt (
SELECT x, SUM(grp_cnt) AS x_cnt
FROM grp_cnt
GROUP BY x
ORDER BY x_cnt DESC
LIMIT ${limit}
)
SELECT *
FROM grp_cnt JOIN x_cnt USING (x)
ORDER BY x_cnt DESC
